dct_title_s: Boro of Red Bank, Map showing location of Proposed Sewage Treatment Plant and of Lands to be Acquire from State of NJ and from C.E. Conover Co.
dct_description_sm: A map showing the proposed layout of industrial spaces to be developed by the C.E. Conover Company along the Navesink River in Red Bank, New Jersey.
